docs {
  ## Get Vendor
  ดึงข้อมูลผู้ขายรายการเดียวตาม ID
  
  Retrieves a single vendor/supplier record by its unique identifier.


  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "code": "VND-001",
      "name": "Vendor Name",
      "description": "Vendor description",
      "note": "...",
      "business_type": {},
      "tax_profile_id": "uuid",
      "tax_profile_name": "VAT 7%",
      "tax_rate": 0.07,
      "is_active": true,
      "info": [],
      "vendor_address": [],
      "vendor_contact": [],
      "created_at": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

